au14-trait-panicprone-name = Panic Prone
au14-trait-panicprone-desc = Panic builds gradually when you're struck by gunfire, take a serious wound, get knocked down by an explosion, or see someone nearby die. Once your composure breaks you'll start letting out involuntary screams and your aim will worsen. It fades over time if you're left alone.
au14-panicprone-warn = Your heart is pounding.
au14-panicprone-peak = You can't stop shaking!
au14-panicprone-calming = Your heart rate settles, but you're still shaken.
